      <subfield code="a">Machine generated contents note: 1. Inheriting loss: Mary Sidney Herbert, Countess of Pembroke; 2. The golden chain: Aemelia Lanyer; 3. 'This testament of me': Mary Wroth's melancholic sonnets; 4. 'In every breast her monument': Katherine Philips.</subfield>
